{"tid":628777,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉襲「愛國」者　長毛轟政治檢控","createTime":"2018-04-14T07:15:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T07:34:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f458eef7588c642f0b30b265df8aa460086db4d7","tid":628777,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T07:15:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361118?_ga=2.141215538.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361118%3F_ga%3D2.141215538.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=o8Ll8V75HeyJumkgqsKAXcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=332b9a12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180414%2F20361118%3F_ga%3D2.141215538.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=6aecee79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180414/20361118?_ga=2.141215538.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n涉襲「愛國」者　長毛轟政治檢控<br />\n<br />\n1.4K<br />\n法庭<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180414/large/a12a02a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180414%2Flarge%2Fa12a02a.gif&h=d07241f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n梁國雄昨指執法親疏有別，放生梁振英；小圖為事主劉必泉。<br />\n李潤芳攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】社民連「長毛」梁國雄去年4月12日仍是立法會議員時，在立法會外接收請願信期間，與一名「愛國」團體成員糾纏，事隔一年後，梁被控普通襲擊罪，昨在東區裁判法院提堂。梁不認罪，案件押後至5月14日進行審前覆核聆訊。梁在庭外批評有關部門執法親疏有別，他被政治檢控，梁振英涉UGL事件卻逍遙法外。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警freelancer當裝修工<br />\n<br />\n62歲的梁國雄被指當日在立法會綜合大樓外襲擊劉必泉。劉正是去年1月有份於香港機場包圍從台灣返港的時任立法會議員羅冠聰，經審訊後被裁定非法集結罪成，判囚3個月，現保釋等候上訴。自行代表的梁在庭上稱，昨早才取得控方文件，需時閱讀，他亦要聯絡案發時就全民退保請願的人士，以便傳召他們作辯方證人。<br />\n<br />\n此外，控罪書指梁報稱任職裝修工人，梁昨解釋，他向警員稱任職freelancer（自由工作者），但警員卻自創填上裝修工人，梁笑言：「差人做嘢係咁，無傷大雅。」<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC883/18<br />\n■記者黃幗慧"},{"pid":"d1387950a2ce252f48f327bd8826a3e5ca382b60","tid":628777,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T07:31:36.000Z","msg":"樓主硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99d068f310b80df667e5efc8cb328bb37a121edf","tid":628777,"uid":10296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T07:34:02.000Z","msg":"Mo哥做裝修佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}